        <label>1: LED Indicator</label>
        <description><![CDATA[
LED Indicator ON/OFF/Disabled<br /><h1>Overview</h1><p>LED Indicator ON/OFF/Disabled<br />00==Plug On / LED On<br />01==Plug On / LED Off<br />02==LED Disabled</p>
        ]]></description>
        <default>0</default>
